    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Transmission received. We've reviewed the logs. Mission Control is concerned that going into permanent hibernation now will result in the loss of the scheduled seasonal drilling window, which is the main objective of this mission. Is there any way to adjust your operational parameters to stay active without triggering a critical battery failure?",
